| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2228 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 856aa4af-7ce6-5936-a54f-1e1036cb5f73"
